article_title: Nina Dobrev Goes Topless For The Affordable Care Act –
article_text:
The Vampire Diaries actress makes a unique statement in support of Obamacare. Nina Dobrev posted a photo on Instagram of herself topless with a sign covering her lady parts that read #getCovered, with the following message.

“Im Canadian. We have healthcare for all,” the 24-year-old TV star explained in the caption. “If you dont have insurance go to http://say.ly/cdi6TN2 and #GetCovered ,Because w/o it, youre naked.”

Check out the full pic below.

Are you convinced to finally get covered?
